name: Tracing A Heart At The Center Of Raw Carnal Love
description:
When everything disappears but you
the memory of you
shapes my experience
and invokes the beasts I see in this darkness
that reminds me
this is about you even when it's not
that reminds me
I still crave your presence
so I trace a heart deep within the raw carnal love
of someone else
and I get lost imagining it is within you I am reborn
and it feels like poison
because this moment is about you
even when it is not
